text: There is a new fishball noodle stall in this coffeeshop. Taste very good. Good amount of vinegar, 2 big fish ball that were fresh and bouncy, 2 big stuff meatballs, 2 fried wanton skin and pork livers. Good bowl of breakfast and lunch meal $5.50. Highly recommend.

Found this Jin Sheng Zha Cai Fan opened here. Their Braised Pork Skin and Pumpkin is the best. Pumpkin not mushy and Pig Skin is delicious. They have few outlet islandwide but surprised to find them there also.
Love the curry chicken so Lemak and fragrance just liked my Mama.
Delicious food at very affordable prices. Vendors were quite friendly and generous with the serving size! Really love their iced milo as its pretty thick!
